verbose_text: Wild-type HRas bound to GppNHp (PDB ID 3K8Y) or GDP (PDB ID 2RGE) with switches I and II removed, were used in molecular replacement as initial phasing models for HRas G13D crystallized with symmetry of the C121 space group, and once solved, this solution was used to phase the other HRas, KRas and NRas GppNHp bound crystal structures.
